transform = Transform3D(1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 11, 2.103, 7)
message = "THE SOURCEPLAIN MONOLITH\n\nLirien shaped this stone before the first dawn,\nand into it pressed the song of every river.\n\nKhorgaul came and took the Sigil.\nThe Source still hums, but only Glim hears it now.\n\n\"What is given freely runs without end.\n What is hoarded, stagnates.\""

